  "time_ut": 1661256128,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dad\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0daf\u0dba \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dc5\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dda \u0db4\u0db1\u0dad \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0da2\u0dcf\u0dad\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0db1\u0ddc\u0dc0\u0db1 \u0d85\u0dba\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0db7\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dad \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dbd\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Prevention of Terrorism Act has been used in an undemocratic manner",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Human Rights Commission of Sri Lanka has issued a statement saying that arresting protesters, detaining them and questioning them under the Prevention of Terrorism Act is an undemocratic use of the Prevention of Terrorism Act.",
        "The same commission informs that it has been used to justify arresting protesters.",
        "It is a matter of concern that the Prevention of Terrorism Act has been used against suspects who are not related to the matters mentioned in the definition of the Terrorism Act, it is stated in the announcement.",
        "It is stated in the announcement that the Human Rights Commission has requested the Inspector General of Police to inform the Human Rights Commission about the facts and circumstances that led to dealing with these suspects under the Prevention of Terrorism Act.",
        "As alleged by the police, the Human Rights Commission wants to ascertain whether there are any reports related to the terrorist acts that have taken place across the country since last January, and the Commission also requests the Commissioner of Police to know about the terrorist acts committed by the arrested suspects.",
        "It is further stated in the announcement issued by the Human Rights Commission that the Human Rights Commission needs to know the identity of the arrested persons and the measures taken to protect the fundamental rights of the suspects detained under the Prevention of Terrorism Act."
      ],
